download - Sample minimal application with custom strings

== Usage ==

  download SOURCE [OPTIONS]
  download --help | -h
  download --version | -v

== Options ==

  --help, -h
    Show this helpful help

  --version, -v
    Show version number

  --out, -o DIR (required)
    Target directory

== Arguments ==

  SOURCE
    URL to download from

